    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is in great shape, showing only minor surface scratches and a few small rock chips consistent with regular highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door panels. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a complete service history. This car is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
