    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. It offers a reliable driving experience with a smooth engine and transmission that shift as they should. While there are minor signs of regular use consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the exterior retains a nice finish. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
